<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef984da4-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s200310"><num value="200310">§ 200310.</num><heading> Transfers to and from Fund</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idef984da5-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s200310/a"><num value="a">(a)</num><heading> <inline class="small-caps">Motorboat Fuel Taxes</inline>.—</heading><content>There shall be set aside in the Fund the amounts specified in section 9503(c)(3)(B) of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 (<ref href="/us/usc/t26/s9503/c/3/B">26 U.S.C. 9503(c)(3)(B)</ref>).</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idef984da6-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s200310/b"><num value="b">(b)</num><heading> <inline class="small-caps">Refunds of Taxes</inline>.—</heading><chapeau>There shall be paid from time to time from the Fund into the general fund of the Treasury amounts estimated by the Secretary of the Treasury as equivalent to—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idef984da7-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s200310/b/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> the amounts paid before <date date="2029-10-01">October 1, 2029</date>, under section 6421 of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 (<ref href="/us/usc/t26/s6421">26 U.S.C. 6421</ref>) with respect to gasoline used after <date date="1964-12-31">December 31, 1964</date>, in motorboats, on the basis of claims filed for periods ending before <date date="2028-10-01">October 1, 2028</date>; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idef984da8-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s200310/b/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> 80 percent of the floor stocks refunds made before <date date="2029-10-01">October 1, 2029</date>, under section 6412(a)(1) of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 (<ref href="/us/usc/t26/s6412/a/1">26 U.S.C. 6412(a)(1)</ref>) with respect to gasoline to be used in motorboats.</content>
</paragraph>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idef984da9-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db">(<ref href="/us/pl/113/287/s3">Pub. L. 113–287, § 3</ref>, <date date="2014-12-19">Dec. 19, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/3179">128 Stat. 3179</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/114/94/dC/tXXXI/s31102/e/2/B">Pub. L. 114–94, div. C, title XXXI, § 31102(e)(2)(B)</ref>, <date date="2015-12-04">Dec. 4, 2015</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/129/1728">129 Stat. 1728</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/117/58/dH/tI/s80102/e/2/B">Pub. L. 117–58, div. H, title I, § 80102(e)(2)(B)</ref>, <date date="2021-11-15">Nov. 15, 2021</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/135/1328">135 Stat. 1328</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
