<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">In subsection (a), the words “(relating to special motor fuels and gasoline used in motorboats)” are omitted as unnecessary.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">In subsection (b), the words “(relating to amounts paid in respect of gasoline used for certain nonhighway purposes or by local transit systems)” are omitted as unnecessary.</p>
