<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2015—Subsec. (b)(1). <ref href="/us/pl/114/94">Pub. L. 114–94</ref> substituted “<date date="2023-10-01">October 1, 2023</date>” for “<date date="2017-10-01">October 1, 2017</date>” and “<date date="2022-10-01">October 1, 2022</date>” for “<date date="2016-10-01">October 1, 2016</date>”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Subsec. (b)(2). <ref href="/us/pl/114/94/s31102/e/2/B/i">Pub. L. 114–94, § 31102(e)(2)(B)(i)</ref>, substituted “<date date="2023-10-01">October 1, 2023</date>” for “<date date="2017-10-01">October 1, 2017</date>”.</p>
</note>
